{"tid":695754,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"范冰冰公司被揭「不存在」","createTime":"2018-06-09T12:48:53.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T13:21:41.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"b6e7f9a6090ead56afd71e568e4fdfa2e3015871","tid":695754,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:48:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180609/20415522\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180609%2F20415522&d=9HWljdMLh3TnBmMR72HZFf%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=18f04ed4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180609%2F20415522&h=b40d440f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180609/20415522</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年06月09日 <br />\n<br />\n范冰冰公司被揭「不存在」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180609/large/09la1p901.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180609%2Flarge%2F09la1p901.jpg&h=0adb4ec2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n范冰冰<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】范冰冰現時最少可查證直接或間接持有20間公司，不過她的公司被內媒指問題多多，媒體揭發她虛報公司地址，前天更直擊其新疆霍爾果斯的公司，發現根本無人辦公。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180609/large/a0102a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180609%2Flarge%2Fa0102a.gif&h=a18f0ac3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n <br />\n新疆公司無人辦公<br />\n<br />\n現時無錫地稅局亦暗示調查明星涉嫌避稅逃稅，范冰冰4間公司在無錫註冊，包括無錫唐德文化傳媒、無錫愛美神影視文化，以及無錫美濤佳藝影視文化，全部註冊地址都在無錫蠡湖大道2009號無錫國家數字電影產業園，但《每日經濟新聞》記者曾走遍產業園，都找不到上述3間公司的辦公室。《新京報》前天亦直擊新疆霍爾果斯，范的公司註冊在當地亞歐路商貿中心三樓，該商貿中心是一座3層高的商場，一樓、二樓賣進口食品、服裝、化妝品，三樓只有一間大型家具城。家具城人員指，除家具城外，三樓的另一片區域沒有人辦公。<br />\n <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180609/large/a0102b.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180609%2Flarge%2Fa0102b.gif&h=2f000d20&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n馮小剛也被揭發名下有多達21間公司，包括影視娛樂、廣告類企業，還有少數科技、馬術等投資企業，身家至少24億港元。他的浙江東陽美拉傳媒有限公司在2015年被軍方背景的華誼兄弟收購，一次過袋走了10億元（約12.8億港元），收購完成後兩間公司股價同樣狂升，其後馮在股票市場減持賺錢。他的公司在2020年才完成與華誼兄弟的對賭協議。<br />\n<br />\n■記者黎仕南  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n逃稅風暴　習帝整頓娛圈　下電影禁軍令　軍方撐腰《戰狼2》《紅海行動》遭狠批<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n驊威36億購「兩劇公司」惹質疑<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n驊威36億購「兩劇公司」惹質疑<br />\n<br />\n【逃稅風暴】行動撐崔永元 深圳驚現「丐幫」主動交稅<br />\n<br />\n逃稅風暴習帝整頓娛圈　下電影禁軍令軍方撐腰《戰狼2》《紅海行動》遭狠批"},{"pid":"1c6dc85a6dadbc0a18432235ea98e0fc8592f0d7","tid":695754,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:50:04.000Z","msg":"高級人頭 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"216b7d92ce4401fde3cf08f9d1aed342e719aef4","tid":695754,"uid":6192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:53:05.000Z","msg":"完美演譯咩叫棄卒"},{"pid":"7c29583ff582559dc68d9a7e1c0fb25fae2897ac","tid":695754,"uid":5489,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-09T12:59:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://timgsa.baidu.com/timg?image&amp;quality=80&amp;size=b9999_10000&amp;sec=1528559211345&amp;di=509e199f640c342af250e1f7510de01a&amp;imgtype=0&amp;src=http%3A%2F%2Fimage.guang.j.cn%2Fimages%2Fcss%2Fstatic%2Fqiuzhuang%2Fimgs%2Fimages%2Fmingxing%2F1211%2Fmx_logo.jpg%3Fv%3D1491810378\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftimgsa.baidu.com%2Ftimg%3Fimage%26quality%3D80%26size%3Db9999_10000%26sec%3D1528559211345%26di%3D509e199f640c342af250e1f7510de01a%26imgtype%3D0%26src%3Dhttp%253A%252F%252Fimage.guang.j.cn%252Fimages%252Fcss%252Fstatic%252Fqiuzhuang%252Fimgs%252Fimages%252Fmingxing%252F1211%252Fmx_logo.jpg%253Fv%253D1491810378&h=040b7ff3&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fa30e6cdf8a62b7e8ccca88144d8779